title: Sooo im level 30, but this site says im level 3..........

replies.body: I had the same thing, i posted that my account is for some reason stuck on lvl 5, within like 10 minutes it was fine, and then next day it appeared as lvl 5 for like 10 seconds again and then back to 22. Its just sync(o de mayo) problem with the forum, dont bother. Refreshing a couple of times alone should fix it
It looks like your boards profile just needed to resync with your Summoner level. After posting here, you're now showing up as level 30 ^_^.
